data.description: Study of choreography created by member of the faculty and guest artists, leading to public performance. Must be cast in the Faculty Concert or Guest Artist work, and concurrently enrolled in one of the following: DANCE  111, 112, 115, 118, 125, 126, 211, 212, 213, 218 225, 226, 231, 311, 312, 325, or 326. Open to first-year students.
